🔹 BIT 1: Strong ACP Foundations (System + OS + Networking)
This is your base. Without this, SAP BASIS will feel difficult.
🧠 What to learn:
Linux basics
Commands: ls, cd, top, df, du, ps, chmod
File system, permissions
Networking basics
IP, DNS, Subnetting
Ports (HTTP 80, HTTPS 443, SAP 32xx, 36xx)
Server concepts
CPU, RAM, Disk, Virtual Machines
Monitoring basics
CPU usage, memory usage, logs
🎯 Goal:
👉 You should be comfortable working on a Linux server via terminal
